<% content_for(:page_title) { I18n.t("pages.resources.page_title") } %>
<div class="p-4 xl:p-8 xl:py-10" x-data="{showWelshResources: true}">
  <div class="flex justify-around">
    <div class="md:w-1/2 mb-10">
      <h1 class="md:text-4xl text-4xl">🌟<%= t('pages.resources.title') %>🌟</h1>
      <p class="mb-4">
        <%= t('pages.resources.text') %>
      </p>
      <a href="#" x-show="!showWelshResources" class="cursor-pointer link" @click.prevent="$event.preventDefault()" @click="showWelshResources = true">
        <%= t('pages.resources.welsh_resources') %>      
      </a>
      <a href="#" x-show="showWelshResources" class="cursor-pointer link" @click.prevent="$event.preventDefault()" @click="showWelshResources = false">
        <%= t('pages.resources.english_resources') %>
      </a>
    </div>
  </div>
  <div x-show="showWelshResources" class="md:w-1/2 mx-auto">
    <h2 class="text-3xl">🛡️ Your built-in support in Wales 🛡️</h2>
    <p class="mb-1">
      Every family in Wales has access to free support.
    </p>
    <p>Start here if you’re unsure where to go:</p>
    <h3 class="text-2xl mt-6 mb-2">
      👩‍⚕️ Your Health Visitor
    </h3>
    <p class="mb-1">
      Your main point of contact. 
    </p>
    <p>
      👉 If you’re worried about anything, contact your Health Visitor first.
    </p>
    <h3 class="text-2xl mt-6 mb-2">
      📈 Child Development Checks
    </h3>
    <p class="mb-1">
      All families are supported by the <a href="https://www.abbhealthiertogether.cymru.nhs.uk/professionals/health-visitors/healthy-child-programme">Healthy Child Wales Programme</a>.
    </p>
    <p class="mb-1">
      This means you’ll have <strong>planned check-ins with your Health Visiting team</strong> as your child grows. These usually happen around key times, such as during pregnancy, when baby is born, 6 months, and beyond.
    </p>
    <h4 class="font-bold mt-4 mb-1">
      Guidance and Support for Parents
    </h4>
    <p class="mb-1">
      <a href="https://www.gov.wales/parenting-give-it-time" target="_blank">Parenting. Give it Time</a> → Welsh Government resource that offers both:
    </p>
    <ul class="list-disc ml-6 mb-4">
      <li>
        <a href="https://www.gov.wales/parenting-give-it-time/your-childs-development" target="_blank" class="link">Understanding Your Child’s Development</a> – clear guidance on what to expect from ages 0–5, with tips to support each stage
      </li>
      <li>
        Trusted Parenting Advice – practical, non-judgmental support on common topics such as sleeping and feeding
      </li>
    </ul>
    <p>
      👉 If something is worrying you, you can contact your Health Visitor team at any time. You don’t need to wait for a review.
    </p>
    <h3 class="text-2xl mt-6 mb-2">
      👨‍👩‍👧 Finding local support
    </h3>
    <ul class="list-disc ml-6 mb-4">
      <li>
        <a href="https://www.gov.wales/find-your-local-family-information-service" target="_blank" class="link">Family Information Service (FIS)</a> → your local FIS can give you in-depth advice on childcare, funding, and support for families
      </li>
      <li>
        <a href="https://www.dewis.wales/" target="_blank" class="link">Dewis Cymru</a> → a wider, self-service directory covering general wellbeing, local activities, and community support across Wales
      </li>
      <li>
        Local libraries → free activities, parent support and community hubs
      </li>
    </ul>
    <h3 class="text-2xl mt-6 mb-2">
      🌱 Extra support (if eligible)
    </h3>
    <ul class="list-disc ml-6 mb-4">
      <li>
        <a href="https://www.gov.wales/flying-start-guide-parents-and-carers" target="_blank" class="link">Flying Start (Dechrau’n Deg)</a> can offer:
        <ul class="list-disc ml-6 mb-4">
          <li>Free childcare (from age 2)</li>
          <li>Parenting support</li>
          <li>Speech & language help</li>
        </ul>
      </li>
    </ul>
    <p>
      👉 Ask your Health Visitor or <a href="https://www.gov.wales/find-your-local-family-information-service" target="_blank" class="link">FIS</a> if this applies to you.
    </p>
    <h2 class="text-3xl mt-8">➕For everyday challenges ➕</h2>
    <p class="mb-1">
      You can explore these if you want tailored support or have a specific concern:
    </p>
    <h3 class="text-2xl mt-6 mb-2">
      💬 I’m worried about my child’s talking or communication
    </h3>
    <p class="mb-1">
      Start here:
    </p>
    <ul class="list-disc ml-6 mb-4">
      <li>
        Visit <a href="https://www.gov.wales/talk-with-me" target="_blank" class="link">Talk with Me</a> (Siarad Gyda Fi) → tips and activities
      </li>
      <li>
        Your health visitor (see above)
      </li>
    </ul>
    <p>
      You can also:
    </p>
    <ul class="list-disc ml-6 mb-4">
      <li>
        Contact your local NHS Speech & Language Therapy team (no GP needed in most areas)
      </li>
      <li>
        Call NHS 111 Wales if you’re unsure how
      </li>
    </ul>
    <p>
      Helpful resources:
    </p>
    <ul class="list-disc ml-6 mb-4">
      <li>
        <a href="https://speechandlanguage.org.uk/" target="_blank" class="link">Speech and Language UK</a> → advice on speech & language needs
      </li>
      <li>
        Local libraries → free Story & Song sessions
      </li>
    </ul>
    <h3 class="text-2xl mt-6 mb-2">
      🧠 I’m feeling overwhelmed or worried about mental health
    </h3>
    <p class="mb-1">
      If you need to talk now (24/7):
    </p>
    <ul class="list-disc ml-6 mb-4">
      <li>
        Call 111 (press Option 2)
      </li>
      <li>
        <a href="https://www.callhelpline.org.uk/" target="_blank" class="link">C.A.L.L.</a> Helpline → call or text support, in either English or Welsh
      </li>
    </ul>
    <p>
      Ongoing support:
    </p>
    <ul class="list-disc ml-6 mb-4">
      <li>Your GP</li>
      <li><a href="https://www.mind.org.uk/about-us/mind-cymru/" target="_blank" class="link">Mind Cymru</a></li>
      <li><a href="https://parents.actionforchildren.org.uk/parent-talk-cymru/" target="_blank" class="link">Parent Talk Cymru</a> → chat with a parenting coach via Whatsapp</li>
    </ul>
    <h3 class="text-2xl mt-6 mb-2">
      😩 My child cries a lot or feels hard to manage
    </h3>
    <ul class="list-disc ml-6 mb-4">
      <li>
        <a href="https://www.cry-sis.org.uk/" target="_blank" class="link">Cry-sis</a> → support with crying and sleepless babies
      </li>
      <li>
        <a href="https://parents.actionforchildren.org.uk/parent-talk-cymru/" target="_blank" class="link">Parent Talk Cymru</a> → chat with a parenting coach via Whatsapp
      </li>
      <li>
        <a href="https://www.annafreud.org/" target="_blank" class="link">Anna Freud Centre</a> → parent guides to support a child experiencing mental health difficulties
      </li>
    </ul>
    <h3 class="text-2xl mt-6 mb-2">
      🧸 I want ideas to support my child’s development
    </h3>
    <p>
      Easy, everyday ideas:
    </p>
    <ul class="list-disc ml-6 mb-4">
      <li>
        <a href="https://www.bbc.co.uk/cbeebies/parenting" target="_blank" class="link">CBeebies Parenting</a>
      </li>
      <li>
        <a href="https://www.playfulchildhoods.wales/" target="_blank" class="link">Play Wales</a>
      </li>
    </ul>

    <h3 class="text-2xl mt-6 mb-2">
      🏴 I want to raise my child with Welsh
    </h3>
    <ul class="list-disc ml-6 mb-4">
      <li>
        <a href="https://meithrin.cymru/irieni/?lang=en" target="_blank" class="link">Mudiad Meithrin</a> → playgroups + support
      </li>
      <li>
        <a href="https://meithrin.cymru/cymraeg-for-kids/?lang=en" target="_blank" class="link">Cymraeg i Blant</a>
      </li>
      <li>
        <a href="https://www.gov.wales/talk-with-me" target="_blank" class="link">Talk with Me (Siarad Gyda Fi)</a> → tips and activities
      </li>
    </ul>

    <h3 class="text-2xl mt-6 mb-2">
      💰 I’m worried about money or benefits
    </h3>
    <p>
      Check what you're entitled to
    </p>
    <ul class="list-disc ml-6 mb-4">
      <li>
        <a href="https://www.turn2us.org.uk/" target="_blank" class="link">Turn2us</a>
      </li>
      <li>
        <a href="https://advicelinkcymru.org.uk/" target="_blank" class="link">Advicelink Cymru</a>
      </li>
    </ul>

    <p>
      Speak to someone
    </p>
    <ul class="list-disc ml-6 mb-4">
      <li>
        <a href="https://www.citizensadvice.org.uk/" target="_blank" class="link">Citizens Advice Wales</a>
      </li>
    </ul>

    <p>
      Additional support
    </p>
    <ul class="list-disc ml-6 mb-4">
      <li>
        <a href="https://applyforhealthystart.nhsbsa.nhs.uk/apply-for-healthy-start/" target="_blank" class="link">Healthy Start Scheme</a> → help with food costs
      </li>
    </ul>

    <h3 class="text-2xl mt-6 mb-2">
      🚨 I need urgent help
    </h3>
    <ul class="list-disc ml-6 mb-4">
      <li>
        <strong>Call 999</strong> → life-threatening emergency
      </li>
      <li>
        <strong>Call 111</strong> → urgent medical help
      </li>
    </ul>
    <p>Emotional support (24/7):</p>
    <ul class="list-disc ml-6 mb-4">
      <li>
        Samaritans Cymru → call 116 123
      </li>
    </ul>

    <p>Not sure where to start?</p>
    <p>
      Begin with your Health Visitor or Family Information Service. They’ll help you find the right next step!
    </p>
  </div>

  <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-5" x-show="!showWelshResources">
    <div class="bg-pink-100 p-8 col-span-1">
      <h2>🧠 <%= t('pages.resources.england.mental_health.title') %></h2>
      <ul>
